# Program 5: write a program to take input from user
## Program 5 : Write a program using conditional operators

```
#include<stdio.h>

int main()

{

    int a;

    printf("enter an integer:");

    scanf("%d", &a);

    printf("number= %d",a);

    return 0;

int T=90,P=90,c;
c=(T>80&&P>80)?1000:(P>80)?500:0;
printf("%d",c);
return 0;
}

# Output:

enter an integer:

43

number=43

```
**Output : 1000**
